To join the Tortoise channel:Sign Up for Farcaster: Create an account via farcaster.xyz or Warpcast, using “Sign in with Farcaster” (SIWF) for wallet-based authentication.

Follow Tortoise: Visit https://farcaster.xyz/~/channel/tortoise or find it in Warpcast’s channel list. Click “Follow” to see its casts in your feed.
Cast Thoughtfully: Create a cast, select Tortoise as the channel, and agree to its norms. Share an idea, question, or insight to spark discussion.
Explore Mini Apps: Use bots like @perl
 or @mintit
 to enhance your experience, or check out analytics tools like CastSense for deeper insights into the channel’s activity.
